attributes: {"filter":"","mode":"query","Query":"SELECT \\n    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY mj.start_time ASC) AS 'S.No', \\n    mj.job_name AS 'Job Name', \\n    DATE_FORMAT(mj.start_time, '%d-%m-%Y %H:%i:%s') AS 'Start Datetime',\\n    CAST(ROUND(mp.predicted_duration) AS SIGNED) AS 'Estimated Time (mins)',\\n    TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, mj.start_time, CONVERT_TZ(NOW(),'+00:00', '+05:30')) AS 'Execution Time till now (mins)',\\n    CAST(TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, mj.start_time, CONVERT_TZ(NOW(),'+00:00', '+05:30')) - mp.predicted_duration AS SIGNED) AS 'Delay (mins)'\\nFROM \\n    iegp_ml_dev.ml_jobdata mj \\nINNER JOIN \\n    iegp_ml_dev.ml_jobprediction mp ON mj.id = mp.job_id \\nWHERE \\n    mj.is_predicted = 1\\n    AND mj.start_time < CONVERT_TZ(NOW(),'+00:00', '+05:30')\\n    AND mj.end_time IS NULL\\n    AND TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, mj.start_time, CONVERT_TZ(NOW(),'+00:00', '+05:30')) > mp.predicted_duration\\nORDER BY \\n    mj.start_time ASC \\nLIMIT 50;","Cacheable":false,"isStreaming":"false","Headers":"","defaultValues":"","QueryParams":"","writeMode":"append","params":"{'startDate':start_time,'endDate':start_time}","tableName":"","uniqueIdentifier":""}

attributes: {"filter":"","mode":"query","Query":"SELECT \\n\\tmj.job_name AS 'Job Name',\\n        mj.start_time AS 'Start DateTime',\\n\\tmj.end_time AS 'End DateTime',\\n\\tmp.actual_status AS 'Actual Status',\\n\\tmp.predicted_status AS 'Predicted Status',\\n\\tmp.actual_duration AS 'Actual Duration in (mins)',\\n\\tmp.predicted_duration AS 'Predicted Duration in (mins)'\\n\\t\\nFROM \\n    iegp_ml_dev.ml_jobdata mj \\nINNER JOIN \\n    iegp_ml_dev.ml_jobprediction mp ON mj.id = mp.job_id \\nWHERE \\n mj.end_time IS NOT NULL\\nORDER BY \\nmj.end_time DESC","Cacheable":false,"isStreaming":"false","Headers":"","defaultValues":"","QueryParams":"","writeMode":"append","params":"{'startDate':mj.start_time,'endDate':mj.start_time}","tableName":"","uniqueIdentifier":""}

attributes: {"filter":"","mode":"query","Query":"SELECT \\n        CASE\\n            WHEN DATEDIFF({endDate}, {startDate}) < 10 THEN DATE_FORMAT(mj.start_time, '%d-%m-%Y') \\n            WHEN DATEDIFF({endDate}, {startDate}) BETWEEN 10 AND 31 THEN CONCAT(\\n                DATE_FORMAT(DATE_SUB(mj.start_time, INTERVAL WEEKDAY(mj.start_time) DAY), '%d-%b'), \\n                ' to ', \\n                DATE_FORMAT(DATE_ADD(mj.start_time, INTERVAL 6-WEEKDAY(mj.start_time) DAY), '%d-%b')\\n            ) \\n            WHEN DATEDIFF({endDate}, {startDate}) BETWEEN 31 AND 365 THEN DATE_FORMAT(mj.start_time, '%m-%Y') \\n            ELSE DATE_FORMAT(mj.start_time, '%Y')\\n        END AS JobDate,\\n    IFNULL(\\n        ROUND(\\n            (\\n                SUM(\\n                    CASE \\n                        WHEN mj.end_time IS NOT NULL \\n                             AND mp.actual_status = mp.predicted_status \\n                        THEN 1 \\n                        ELSE 0 \\n                    END\\n                ) / NULLIF(\\n                    SUM(CASE WHEN mj.end_time IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END), 0\\n                ) * 100\\n            ), \\n        1), \\n    'NA') AS 'Prediction Accuracy' \\nFROM iegp_ml_dev.ml_jobdata mj\\nINNER JOIN iegp_ml_dev.ml_jobprediction mp ON mj.id = mp.job_id \\nWHERE   \\n    mj.is_predicted = 1 AND mj.end_time IS NOT NULL  AND (mj.start_time BETWEEN {startDate} AND {endDate}) GROUP BY JobDate ORDER BY JobDate ASC","Cacheable":false,"isStreaming":"false","Headers":"","defaultValues":"","QueryParams":"","writeMode":"append","params":"{'startDate':\\"'2024-11-10 00:00:00'\\",'endDate':\\"'2024-11-19 00:00:00'\\"}","tableName":"","uniqueIdentifier":""}

attributes: {"filter":"","mode":"query","Query":"SELECT \\n        CASE\\n            WHEN DATEDIFF({endDate}, {startDate}) < 10 THEN DATE_FORMAT(origin_datetime, '%d-%m-%Y')  \\n            WHEN DATEDIFF({endDate}, {startDate}) BETWEEN 10 AND 31 THEN CONCAT(DATE_FORMAT(DATE_SUB(origin_datetime, INTERVAL WEEKDAY(origin_datetime) DAY), '%d-%b'), ' to ', DATE_FORMAT(DATE_ADD(origin_datetime, INTERVAL 6-WEEKDAY(origin_datetime) DAY), '%d-%b')) \\n            WHEN DATEDIFF({endDate}, {startDate}) BETWEEN 32 AND 365 THEN DATE_FORMAT(origin_datetime, '%m-%Y')  \\n            ELSE DATE_FORMAT(origin_datetime, '%Y')  \\n        END  AS Date,\\n    COUNT(id) AS Ticketcount \\nFROM iegp_ml_dev.ml_ticketdata  \\nWHERE   \\n    (origin_datetime BETWEEN {startDate} AND {endDate})\\n    AND train_to_model = 0 \\nGROUP BY Date \\nORDER BY Date ASC;","Cacheable":false,"isStreaming":"false","Headers":"","defaultValues":"","QueryParams":"","writeMode":"append","params":"{'startDate':\\"'2020-03-21 17:31:01'\\",'endDate':\\"'2024-12-31 00:00:00'\\"}","tableName":"","uniqueIdentifier":""}

attributes: {"filter":"","mode":"query","Query":"SELECT \\n        CASE\\n            WHEN DATEDIFF({endDate}, {startDate}) < 10 THEN DATE_FORMAT(md.origin_datetime, '%d-%m-%Y') \\n            WHEN DATEDIFF({endDate}, {startDate}) BETWEEN 10 AND 31 THEN CONCAT(DATE_FORMAT(DATE_SUB(md.origin_datetime, INTERVAL WEEKDAY(md.origin_datetime) DAY), '%d-%b'), ' to ', DATE_FORMAT(DATE_ADD(md.origin_datetime, INTERVAL 6-WEEKDAY(md.origin_datetime) DAY), '%d-%b')) \\n            WHEN DATEDIFF({endDate}, {startDate}) BETWEEN 31 AND 365 THEN DATE_FORMAT(md.origin_datetime, '%m-%Y') \\n            ELSE DATE_FORMAT(md.origin_datetime, '%Y')  \\n        END  AS Date,\\n    COUNT(mp.ticket_id) AS Ticketcount \\nFROM iegp_ml_dev.ml_ticketdata md \\nINNER JOIN iegp_ml_dev.ml_ticketprediction mp ON md.id = mp.ticket_id \\nWHERE   \\n    md.origin_datetime >= {startDate} \\n    AND md.origin_datetime <= {endDate} \\n    AND mp.predicted_assignmentgroup IS NOT NULL \\n\\tAND mp.predicted_assignee IS NOT NULL\\n    AND md.train_to_model = 0 \\n\\tAND md.closed_date IS NULL \\nGROUP BY Date \\nORDER BY Date ASC;","Cacheable":false,"isStreaming":"false","Headers":"","defaultValues":"","QueryParams":"","writeMode":"append","params":"{'startDate':\\"'2020-03-21 17:31:01'\\",'endDate':\\"'2024-12-31 00:00:00'\\"}","tableName":"","uniqueIdentifier":""}

attributes: {"filter":"","mode":"query","Query":"SELECT \\n        CASE\\n            WHEN DATEDIFF({endDate}, {startDate}) < 10 THEN DATE_FORMAT(mj.origin_datetime, '%d-%m-%Y') \\n            WHEN DATEDIFF({endDate}, {startDate}) BETWEEN 10 AND 31 THEN CONCAT(\\n                DATE_FORMAT(DATE_SUB(mj.origin_datetime, INTERVAL WEEKDAY(mj.origin_datetime) DAY), '%d-%b'), \\n                ' to ', \\n                DATE_FORMAT(DATE_ADD(mj.origin_datetime, INTERVAL 6-WEEKDAY(mj.origin_datetime) DAY), '%d-%b')\\n            ) \\n            WHEN DATEDIFF({endDate}, {startDate}) BETWEEN 31 AND 365 THEN DATE_FORMAT(mj.origin_datetime, '%m-%Y') \\n            ELSE DATE_FORMAT(mj.origin_datetime, '%Y')\\n        END AS Date,\\n    IFNULL(\\n        ROUND(\\n            (\\n                SUM(\\n                    CASE \\n                        WHEN  mj.origin_datetime IS NOT NULL AND\\n                              mp.predicted_assignmentgroup = mp.actual_assignmentgroup \\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t  AND mp.actual_assignee = mp.predicted_assignee\\n                        THEN 1 \\n                        ELSE 0 \\n                    END\\n                ) / NULLIF(\\n                    SUM(CASE WHEN mj.origin_datetime IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END), 0\\n                ) * 100\\n            ), \\n        1), \\n    'NA') AS 'Prediction Accuracy' \\nFROM ml_ticketdata mj\\nINNER JOIN ml_ticketprediction mp ON mj.id = mp.ticket_id \\nWHERE   \\n    mj.train_to_model = 0 AND mj.closed_date IS NULL  AND (mj.origin_datetime BETWEEN {startDate} AND {endDate}) GROUP BY Date ORDER BY Date ASC;","Cacheable":false,"isStreaming":"false","Headers":"","defaultValues":"","QueryParams":"","writeMode":"append","params":"{'startDate':\\"'2020-03-21 17:31:01'\\",'endDate':\\"'2024-12-31 00:00:00'\\"}","tableName":"","uniqueIdentifier":""}
